        "username": "wll",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.foundationdb.org/wll/{size}/386_2.png",
        "created_at": "2018-10-17T15:08:07.933Z",
        "cooked": "<ol>\n<li>Does satellite automatically repair primary (and vice versa)?</li>\n<li>Is there a change in requirements for satellites (due to no storage servers) (e.g., less than 4GB RAM per <code>fdbserver</code>)?</li>\n<li>How much space would the combination of <code>single</code> and <a href=\"https://github.com/apple/foundationdb/blob/release-6.0/fdbclient/DatabaseConfiguration.cpp#L85\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><code>one_satellite_single</code></a> modes (2 DCs) save compared to <code>double</code> mode (1 DC)?</li>\n</ol>",
